 137:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_spi.c ****        When the compilation define USE_HAL_PPP_REGISTER_CALLBACKS is set to 0 or
 138:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_spi.c ****        not defined, the callback registering feature is not available
 139:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_spi.c ****        and weak (surcharged) callbacks are used.
